long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Stick Merge Master Class is an engaging blend of casual action ğŸ® and strategic merging gameplay, designed by the creative minds at TinyDobbins.

In this game, your mission is to amalgamate diverse weapon types ğŸ”« to forge mightier firearms, which you'll then employ against animated stick figures in a dynamic shooting range environment.

Gear up your arsenal, elevate your handgun's capabilities, discover every power-up ğŸš€ at your disposal, and rise to become the preeminent marksman in the metropolis.

The question at the heart of Stick Merge Master Class is just how formidable you can become. ğŸŒŸ Join us in this adventure to uncover your true potential!
